snippet.title: Rotoscape Demo Promo
snippet.description:
A game about rotating shapes. To save the Shapiverse. Rotoscape is a minimalistic fast-paced action puzzle game about rotating shapes with a soundtrack by Geoplex.
Wishlist today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/663940/Rotoscape

There will be a demo available during the Steam festival on October 7th, 2020. Be on the lookout for that!

Discord: https://discord.gg/MAtA3g8
